\begin_layout Plain Layout

http://www.lilypond.org
\end_layout

\end_inset

 and download it.
 You can also use your distribution package manager to install it on Linux.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For print preview, you should have a working PDF viewer installed on your
 system.
 Use File->Print preview 
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename images/printpreview.png
	scale 40

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
You can print the document directly using the File->Print or you can print
 it indirectly from your PDF viewer application (preferred).
\end_layout

